===Taskbot instance installation & settings===

Required packages:
- Install cygwin with python & screen (https://www.cygwin.com/) with following packages:
  * python
  * gcc
  * screen
  * wget
  * vim
  * google-breakpad-tools
- Install python mysql connector for CYGWIN python (https://dev.mysql.com/doc/connector-python/en/connector-python-installation-binary.html):
  * Under cygwin:
    1. wget http://dev.mysql.com/get/Downloads/Connector-Python/mysql-connector-python-2.1.4.tar.gz
    2. tar xvfz mysql-connector-python-2.1.4.tar.gz
    3. cd mysql-connector-python-2.1.4
    4. python setup.py install

You have to prepare to run & build nx_vms projects:
- https://networkoptix.atlassian.net/wiki/display/SD/Setup+Development+Environment+on+Windows

Prepare to start:
1. Start cygwin
2. Create ~/.my.cnf file:
   [mysql]
   host=<TASKBOT UI HOST>
   user=taskbot
   database=taskbot
   password=taskbot
2. Create taskbot folder
   mkdir ~/taskbot
   cd ~/taskbot
3. Get taskbot
   hg clone ssh://hg@hdw.mx/devtools devtools
4. Run screen.
5. Create new screen for your run (Ctrl-A-C).
6. Run taskbot instance
   cd ~/taskbot/devtools/taskbot/instances/windows
   ./run.sh [<NX_VMS_BRANCH>]
7. [Optional]. Repeat pp. 5-6 for other branches 
8. [Optional]. Add start.bat to Windows startup:
   - in the Run window, type shell:startup to open the Startup folder;
   - in the Startup folder create shortcut to ~/taskbot/devtools/taskbot/instances/windows/start.bat

Dump Tools:
1. Install Windows SDK 10 (contains cdb debugger utility) from
   https://developer.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/downloads/sdk-archive.
2. Download & install procdump utility:
   - Get from https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/sysinternals/dd996900.aspx;
   - Unpack to c:\bin;
   - Add c:\bin to the system environment variables 'Path';
   - Run c:\bin\procdump to accept EULA.
  

